#. type: Plain text
#: website/content/en/releases/9.3R/relnotes.adoc:13
msgid ""
"The release notes for FreeBSD 9.3-RELEASE contain a summary of the changes "
"made to the FreeBSD base system on the 9.3-STABLE development line. This "
"document lists applicable security advisories that were issued since the "
"last release, as well as significant changes to the FreeBSD kernel and "
"userland. Some brief remarks on upgrading are also presented."
msgstr ""

