msgid ""
"The man:bge[4] driver has been updated to support the BCM57764, BCM57767, "
"BCM57782, BCM57786 and BCM57787 "
"chipsets. "
"http://svn.freebsd.org/viewvc/base?view=revision&revision=258967[r258967]"
