#. type: Plain text
#: website/content/en/releases/9.3R/relnotes.adoc:172
msgid ""
"The man:run[4] driver has been updated to support MediaTek/Ralink chipsets "
"RT5370 and "
"RT5372. "
"http://svn.freebsd.org/viewvc/base?view=revision&revision=259457[r259457]"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: website/content/en/releases/9.3R/relnotes.adoc:174
msgid ""
"The man:usb[4] wireless radiotap headers have been realigned, allowing "
"wireless adapters to work on arm, mips, and other similar platforms where "
"alignment is "
"important. "
"http://svn.freebsd.org/viewvc/base?view=revision&revision=259460[r259460]"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: website/content/en/releases/9.3R/relnotes.adoc:176
msgid ""
"The man:run[4] firmware has been updated to version "
"0.33. "
"http://svn.freebsd.org/viewvc/base?view=revision&revision=260119[r260119]"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: website/content/en/releases/9.3R/relnotes.adoc:178
msgid ""
"The man:bxe[4] driver has been merged from `head/`, providing support for "
"Broadcom NetXtreme II 10Gb PCIe "
"adapters. "
"http://svn.freebsd.org/viewvc/base?view=revision&revision=260252[r260252]"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: website/content/en/releases/9.3R/relnotes.adoc:180
msgid ""
"The man:run[4] driver has been updated to include support for the "
"MediaTek/Ralink RT3593 "
"chipset. "
"http://svn.freebsd.org/viewvc/base?view=revision&revision=261865[r261865]"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: website/content/en/releases/9.3R/relnotes.adoc:182
msgid ""
"The man:run[4] driver has been updated to include support for the DLINK "
"DWA-127 wireless "
"adapter. "
"http://svn.freebsd.org/viewvc/base?view=revision&revision=261933[r261933]"
