#. type: Plain text
#: website/content/en/releases/9.3R/relnotes.adoc:186
msgid ""
"The man:urndis[4] driver has been imported from "
"OpenBSD. "
"http://svn.freebsd.org/viewvc/base?view=revision&revision=262362[r262362]"
